Package: lisa
Type: Package
Title: Binned Motif Enrichment Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.6
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dania", "Machlab", email = "dania.machlab@fmi.ch", role = c("aut")),
    person("Lukas", "Burger", email = "lukas.burger@fmi.ch", role = c("aut")),
    person("Michael", "Stadler", email = "michael.stadler@fmi.ch", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Useful functions to bin genomic regions, such as promoters
    or accessible regions, according to a numberical value, such as change of
    expression or accessibility, and identify enriched motifs in each bin.
